snippet.title: Jetha ने खाए Daya के हाथ के मज़ेदार पकवान | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | FE 1389 | 29 Nov 2022
snippet.description:
Episode 1389: Jetha ने खाए Daya के हाथ के मज़ेदार पकवान 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Even after meeting Big B in real life, Gokuldham residents cannot believe that they have witnessed such a historic moment in their lives. Everyone is replaying the moments again and again in their minds and trying to bask in the glory of meeting Amitabh Bachchan in real life. The Gada family is no different with Daya calling her family and telling them all about it. Jetha is enjoying the tasty dishes prepared by Daya.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1389
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #sonypal 

Subscribe to Sony Pal: http:/a/www.youtube.com/sonypalindia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: WOH – Ikka x Dino James x Badshah (Official Lyric Video) | Def Jam India
snippet.description:
India’s Hip-Hop superstars Ikka, Dino James & Badshah come together to channel their inner hopeless romanticism on ‘Woh.’ The track captures the immense hurt, emotions and male vulnerability which comes at the backdrop of a heartbreak. ‘Woh’ is one of the very few records which portray a man’s emotions with evocative honesty and reveals the softer side of him. Dino James pens down the difficulties behind missing someone that he has loved. He feels helpless and apologetic. Ikka feels his heart sinking as he is incapable of fixing the broken relationship and cannot deal with the heartache anymore. Badshah’s verse starts by asserting that it is okay for a man to break down and go through the gut-wrenching feeling of a fleeting romance. ‘Woh’ is an extremely personal track which is bound to shake you if you have ever loved someone.

Stream Now on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/1QUU43rTDMnGl4xyaIfsYN?si=42981c97ba014563

snippet.description:
GondPakRecipe #gondpakrecipe Gond Pak Recipe famous for Gond ke Laddu and Gond ke Barfi. Gond pak is a traditional indian dessert , gond pak made from gond(edible gum), mawa and sugar, gond pak makes every occasion a special one. Gunder pak recipe It is a healthy and tasty winter special Gujarati pak recipe prepared from Gond, dry fruits, coconut, mava, and sugar syrup. Gond Pak is a popular sweet winter snack, made with edible gum (gond) wheat flour and jaggery.

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Portugal 2:0 Uruguay - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Bruno Fernandes scored a sensational goal from a cross-shot as Portugal edged Uruguay in a feisty Group H clash.

After a cagey first-half, Fernandes' curled home from distance & Cristiano Ronaldo appeared to have got something on that. But replays showed the ball went in directly without the skipper's intervention; thus rewarding the Manchester United midfielder his first #FIFAWorldCup goal.

Fernandes then converted his second from the spot after VAR intervened to award the 2016 European champions a penalty following a handball.

2-0 it ended on the night & the result Fernando Santos' side sealed their place in the Round of 16.

snippet.title: Faadu - A Love Story | Pavail Gulati, Saiyami Kher, Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari | Sony LIV Originals
snippet.description:
It was with his brutal honesty, that their story begins.
Faadu is a story about a man belonging to progressive India who lies in the middle of choices that need validation. He is stuck between the fabric of economic upgrade and true love. Abhay, an angry poet and dreamer aspires to reach faster than time from where he can see his rags to riches story. In this ambitious journey of need and greed, he falls in love with Manjiri, a poetess who has a different philosophy about life. In an age where everyone is running behind their ambitious self, will Abhay choose love and simplicity or money and complexity? Faadu answers this very quest of human nature - 'It does not matter where you are born. Your destiny lies in your hands.’ But what if destiny goes completely wrong and you want to go back to where you started?

Produced by StudioNext, Faadu - A Love Story is directed by Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari, written by Saumya Joshi and music composed by Santhosh Narayanan. The Hindi web-series stars Pavail Gulati and Saiyami Kher as Abhay & Manjiri.

Siyani Episode 106 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider - Saniya Shamshad - 29th November 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Siyani Episode 107 Teaser - 29th November 2022 - HAR PAL GEO

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

snippet.title: Episode 517 - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Full Episode | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3628 - 29 Nov 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3628: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak's boss meets him and then heads back to the office, proving that Taarak's alibi worked. The Gokuldham members visit Taarak's residence to find out how they got inside because the boss had been in the society compound the entire time. When Taarak's boss was playing cricket with Tapu Sena and had gone to retrieve the ball from the garden, Jetha tells everyone that Taraak had entered his house successfully. Taarak and Jetha recount the tale of how they managed to enter the house covertly. Anjali explains to everyone that she was concerned since they failed to find the bandage in time. As the group was enjoying the piquant Gulab jamuns that Dr. Hathi had ordered, a man knocked on the door and handed a file that had been provided to him by Taarak's boss. Taarak has been given a couple additional assignments to finish while at home. Watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3628, 29 Nov 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000197274

Sankar points out Thapki and Kabir's absence during the match. When Bihaan goes looking for them, he finds them together in the closet, adding to his hatred for Thapki and Kabir. snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 671 - 29 Nov 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 671: Cheetah Ki Jaan Khatre Mein
--------------------------------------------
Everyone is informed by Karishma Singh that Maddam Sir shot her when he arrived at the scene since Cheetah had already notified Haseena about the Chingaari Gang's plot. When Binny realizes that Cheetah has tricked her, she becomes furious and grabs a gun before running to the police station. She kidnaps Cheetah and takes him to a remote location with the intention of killing him. Cheetah apologizes and expresses her affection to her which convinces her to change her mind and give him a hug. When Shivani and Maddam Sir arrive, they dispute over whether or not to take Binny with them. Watch the episode to know more.
 
Show Name – Maddam Sir
Star Cast –  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No – 671, 29 Nov 2022
Produced By –  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #मैड्डमसर #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3627 - 28 Nov 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3627: 
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak's boss comes to his house and makes his way to Taarak's bedroom to see how he is doing. Everyone tries to stop him, but he succeeds in getting to Taarak this time. Taarak is surprisingly snoozing in his bed while feigning sleep. Everyone follows the boss, so when they discover him lying there, they are shocked. Taarak displays astonishment and acts to be innocent at seeing his boss at his house. The boss now requests that Taarak demonstrate his broken leg. The boss begins to mistrust Taarak as he rips away the blanket from which he had wrapped his leg with Anjali's dupatta. The boss also questions about the leg he was hurt as he had watched it on the video call. Will Taarak be able to use his alibi successfully? Watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3627, 28 Nov 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: YouTube: Learn how misleading emotional words can misinform you
snippet.description:
Misinformation can be hard to identify. 
Have you ever trusted an 'expert' with bogus credentials? 
Shared an article only after reading the headline? 
Most of us may not even realise that we've fallen for misinformation. 
Together, with a few simple tips & skills, we can make our online world a lot safer. Learn how to spot misinformation at youtube.com/HitPauseIndia
